defaultThe British Heart Foundation (BHF) is the nation’s leading heart charity. We are working to achieve our mission of a world in which no-one dies prematurely of heart disease in the UK. We fund ground-breaking medical research, provide support and care to people living with heart disease and advocate for change. We rely on donations from the public to fund our life saving work. 
